Rating: 4
I just returned from Israel and have been craving eggplant dishes like the amazing ones I had there. I like the simple preparation for this very flavorful dish. The fresh dill really brightens it up! I took the advice to use balsamic vinegar instead of red wine vinegar and that worked well. Definitely recommend this dish.

